{"type":"message","id":"002631ff","parentId":"90132d19","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:36:28.920Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-05 22:35:16 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b52137cfeb4a0c2c553887a16b86]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52137cfeb4a0c2c553887a16b86\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-05 22:35 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n你觉得cloude code 源码泄露对openclaw 帮助大吗，有什么可以解决的，有么有人把一些功能作为openclaw的 插件来提供openclaw的能力。"}],"timestamp":1775399788895}}
{"type":"message","id":"25af68e5","parentId":"002631ff","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:36:45.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about:\n1. Whether the Claude Code source code leak is helpful to OpenClaw\n2. What can be done about it\n3. Whether anyone has built plugins for OpenClaw to extend its capabilities\n\nThis is a conversational question about AI/Coding tools and the OpenClaw ecosystem. Let me think about this.\n\nThe user seems to be referring to some kind of \"Claude Code source code leak\" - I should be careful here. I don't have verified information about any \"leak\" of Claude Code's source code. I should not spread unverified claims or speculate about stolen/leaked code.\n\nHowever, the user is asking a legitimate question about:\n\n\n- Whether leaked source code could benefit OpenClaw\n- What OpenClaw's plugin ecosystem looks like\n- Whether people are building extensions for OpenClaw\n\nI know OpenClaw is designed with plugin extensibility in mind - it's an AI coding assistant that can be extended through skills and plugins. Rather than speculating about unverified leaks, I should focus on what I do know about OpenClaw's actual architecture and how it supports extensibility, and I should note that I don't have reliable information about any specific source code leak.","thinkingSignature":"f0c0d37886c80ae1e94f501370966582acdfb3e6dd821bcfc9747b0df399762a"},{"type":"text","text":"这个问题涉及几个方面，我分开说。\n\n**关于\"Claude Code 源码泄露\"**\n我没有看到可靠来源确认这件事。如果有人声称泄露，真实性存疑。你有具体链接或来源吗？\n\n**对 OpenClaw 是否有帮助**\n即使有所谓\"泄露\"，直接参考意义有限：\n- Claude Code 是闭源产品，法律上不可使用\n- 架构思路可以借鉴，但 OpenClaw 已经有自己的设计\n- OpenClaw 的插件体系（Skills）是独立发展的\n\n**OpenClaw 插件生态现状**\n- 官方 Skills 市场：[clawhub.com](https://clawhub.com) — 已经有飞书、天气、搜索等插件\n- 社区 Skills 正在增长\n- 开发者可以用 `skill-creator` 技能自己开发\n\n**你想往哪个方向深挖？**\n- 找现成的 OpenClaw 插件 → 可以去 clawhub.com 搜\n- 想自己开发插件 → 我有 skill-creator 指南\n- 了解 Claude Code 的设计思路做参考 → 这个可以聊\n\n你有具体想做的事吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":473,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":12818,"totalTokens":13330,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0005676,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00480675,"total":0.00538605}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775399788964,"responseId":"0621a66db39827a742b41a88a8a00261"}}
